title: #92Noon! Micheletti/VikingsTalkers/Lavelle/Stefanski
description: Pat Micheletti is in studio on hockey for most of the first hour, Vikings talkers weaved in throughout the show as we look at the AFC North opponents in 2021, Lavelle's weekly 11am(more like 11:05) appearance, and Browns HC Kevin Stefanski joins to end the show!
